  "title": "GUMS: An Accidental Beach Prequel",
  "description": "When LRT bridge construction alters the flow of the river, a giant sturgeon awakens from its slumber to wreak havoc on beach goers trying to enjoy the waist deep waters of the North Saskatchewan River. It's too dangerous, but the Mayor demands the newly formed accidental beach stay open, prompting 3 unexpected heroes to action.",
